Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:15.49,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:19.30,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.95,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}Wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:23.08,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:25.59,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:31.93,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}諦めがくれた安楽 沈滯の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:37.89,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}いつからだっただろうふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:41.18,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}変わらずにいてと願うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:44.88,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}変わりゆく時に生きる僕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.94,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}本當の聲を言う得る夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:52.48,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}君と繋がった空へ響かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:56.38,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}もっと強くこの両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:59.66,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:02.94,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}今度こそは呟く今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:06.12,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:09.52,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}もっと早く君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:12.81,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}たとえ羽根が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:16.10,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}歪む世界 走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:19.38,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:25.15,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5\fad(0,800)}真実と加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:15.49,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}我们在痛楚和泪水的波涛中沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:19.30,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}而我也辗转于种种的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.95,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}唤醒你的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:23.08,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}在苍穹中闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:25.59,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}这是感官的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:31.93,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}放弃所换来的安乐 沉滞的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:37.89,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}是从何时开始的呢 突然放出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:41.18,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}祈祷着不要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:44.88,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}然而我们却活在变迁的时光中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.94,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}真正的心声 形容不出的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:52.48,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}让它们飞往那片与你相连的那片天空 响彻天际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:56.38,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}更加用力 用这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:59.66,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}如能够将泪水全部挥去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:02.94,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}[这次一定]如此低吟的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:06.12,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}即使伤痛也不会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:09.52,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}继续加速 飞往你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:12.81,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}即使我的翅膀四分五裂也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:16.10,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}奔越这扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:19.38,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5}飞往这份感觉的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:25.15,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,	{\blur5\fad(0,800)}向着真实加速
